<p>base.png: 24 pixels of height and just draw it there.</p>
<p>Remember to use the same colors (yellow outline, green skin and so on), they are specified in config.json as fromColors</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fpixeldudesmaker&amp;intent=community">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:572504,&quot;id&quot;:8035530}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-8035530"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fpixeldudesmaker&amp;intent=community"><svg height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fpixeldudesmaker&amp;intent=community"><svg height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/synkrowngames"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyNTczNzEwLnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2FAElby.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/synkrowngames">SynKrown Games</a></span><span title="2023-06-30 09:53:53" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8035530">3 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>i keep getting these odd yellow and green pixels on export. Easy enough to recolor but wondering what could be causing it?<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyNjI3